{"tid":658903,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友係地鐵扯旗","createTime":"2018-05-09T11:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T11:21:28.000Z","uid":80069,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"19d47b84f67aacbe9de841637cf472dd86bcf625","tid":658903,"uid":80069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"前幾日同男朋友諗住落旺角睇鞋，喺地鐵見到鬼婆冇戴bra，粒釘大粒個五蚊銀，可能近排天氣太熱對奶要抖氣。<br />\n男朋友不喜歡穿三角內褲，所謂嘅孖煙通加Nike灰色鬆身短褲，佢話男人嘅浪漫喎。<br />\n我唔知點解佢望兩望都有感覺，之後佢發現下面唔對路跑咗岀去長沙灣站坐喺啲櫈話要冷靜下喎，唔通望兩望當揸咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(錯字不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"0a5f905643bcca3b1aa2745e8ba1d998a87e40a2","tid":658903,"uid":37746,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"人地鍾意大波鬼婆唔鍾意你肥仔波㗎，唔好阻人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf6513c660783467c855cdd7529f52f0cf43ea6","tid":658903,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:20:19.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"6a28a09714dfbed3d745c0759e91cfbe9db78151","tid":658903,"uid":30171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"噤你有冇見到男朋友扯旗而扯旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}